Should you have any questions

00:06:49.210 --> 00:06:53.469
about inventory with ACMP 4,

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:55.210
my collegues and I are

00:06:53.469 --> 00:06:57.370
gladly available to you

00:06:55.210 --> 00:07:00.039
I'd like to thank you for paying attention

00:06:57.370 --> 00:07:03.599
and hope to be welcome you soon to another new ACMP video.

